                Data nomina <lb n="2"/>ad inferas larvas </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Dis Manibus hos <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>oveo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucium</ex></expan> C<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>eli</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Haeb</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="3"/>et si quos alios hos<supplied reason="lost">tes</supplied> <lb n="4"/>habeo <lb n="5"/>neca illa nom<supplied reason="lost">ina</supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bleiernes Fluchtäfelchen, dreieckige Form. Beidseitig beschriftet. Schreibtechnik: geritzt. Kursive Schrift. (B): Audollent: Text 1, Z. 2: ad inferos [---]; Text 2, Z. 2: L. Celi f. haul . m . ua.</p>
